      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in a rare, concours-ready state. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering a linear power band and crisp throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies. The factory Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise, tactile shift throws, paired with a perfectly functioning M-Variable differential lock. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been overhauled, and the rod bearings and subframe reinforcement have been addressed for long-term structural integrity. The chassis remains taut, riding on factory-spec dampening with zero bushing deflection. Finished in a deep luster with an interior devoid of bolster wear, this is a turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
